profile:
Five Star Painting is a locally owned and operated house painting company servicing the West GTA Area.
 
As a part of an international painting franchise system, we give you the peace of mind knowing that we're not a "fly-by-night" contractor that will cut corners or leave the job incomplete. 
 
We provide: 
FREE COLOUR CONSULTATION session with our INTERIOR DESIGNER
PREMIUM ENVIRONMENT-FRIENDLY ZERO VOC PAINTS
 
EXTENDED MANUFACTURER PAINT WARRANTY
EXTENDED LABOUR WARRANTY 
 
QUALIFIED PAINTERS
 
ON-TIME GUARANTEE
BEST PRICE GUARANTEE
 
Thorough Surface Preparation 
A responsive management team should there be any challenges 
Detailed pricing that lets you know what you are getting for your money
 
We are available 24/7 to take your call. Our customer service department will ask for some basic information about your project and will schedule one of our estimators to come out to discuss your project. Our estimators will confirm your appointment, show up on time, and will provide you a detailed quote of the work discussed. It's that simple! 

We are a licensed and insured company that distinguishes our company from smaller and insecure businesses.

We strive to exceed your expectations and focus all of our energy and resources on delivering outstanding results.

Peter’s Painting is a residential interior painting and small commercial interior painting company offering professional interior painting. Servicing areas such as Hamilton, Burlington, Oakville, Mississauga, Ancaster, Brantford, Paris, Cambridge, Kitchener, Grimsby and everywhere in between. 
What makes Peter’s Painting unique? With Peter’s Painting the business owner does the painting. Peter is always on site and in a lot of cases does all the painting himself. From the initial onset when you fill out the Contact Us form, it will be Peter responding to your email, answering your questions, providing you with the estimate, completing the painting for you, and will go over the job with you in full upon completion, ensuring that you are pleased every step of the way. With over a decade of experience painting the hundreds of interiors of homes, we have seen it all and are up to the task to handle whatever your interior painting needs may be. When the business owner does the painting, the homeowner can be assured they have an experienced and professional painter who cares deeply about the aesthetics, longevity, and customer satisfaction of each paint job.

profile:
Green Dragon Construction is a newly formed construction company operating out of Brantford Ontario. Green Dragon was founded with one goal in mind: strive to provide the best quality of work through dedicated craftsmanship and attention to detail. Our dedicated team will ensure that your construction project is done the right way, and also at a reasonable price! No job is too big or small, and Green Dragon is able to complete a wide variety of projects including:
-Painting
-Drywall repair, installation
-Tiles
-Wood floors
-Baseboards and Trim
-Staining and refinishing
-Insulating
-Framing
-Demolition
-Landscape maintenance
-Landscape construction

... and everything in between!

Don't wait! Call or text; 5197712943, Or you can email me, Paul, at paulyoshioka@gmail.com for a free quote today!
